---
import ServiceDetailLayout from "../../layouts/ServiceLayoutDetails.astro";
import { SERVICES } from "../../utils/constants";

const anniversaryService = SERVICES.find(
  (service) => service.slug === "anniversary-shoot"
);

// Additional metadata specifically for Anniversary service
const serviceMetadata = {
  metaDescription:
    "Book our premium themed sets for your Anniversary Photography in Nagpur. Beautiful backdrops, props, and romantic settings at Pixxel City Studio.",
  ogImage:
    "https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/Blue-Jodhpur-5.jpg?updatedAt=1737906079394",
  canonicalUrl: "https://pixxelcity.com/services/anniversary-shoot",
  keywords:
    "anniversary photography sets, venue rental nagpur, photo studio rental, themed backdrops, romantic settings",
};

// Enhance the service object with additional metadata
const enhancedService = {
  ...anniversaryService,
  ...serviceMetadata,
  heroImage:
    "https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/Blue-Jodhpur-5.jpg?updatedAt=1737906079394",
  process: [
    {
      title: "Set Consultation",
      description:
        "We begin with understanding the significance of your anniversary and helping you select the perfect themed set for your celebration photos.",
    },
    {
      title: "Venue Booking",
      description:
        "Choose your preferred date and time slot with package options tailored to the amount of studio time you need.",
    },
    {
      title: "Set Preparation",
      description:
        "Before your arrival, we prepare all sets, props, and special requests to ensure everything is ready for your shoot.",
    },
    {
      title: "Day of the Shoot",
      description:
        "Enjoy exclusive access to your chosen sets with comfortable amenities including changing rooms and refreshments.",
    },
    {
      title: "Support During Session",
      description:
        "Our staff remains available throughout your booking to assist with set changes, props, and any other needs that arise.",
    },
  ],
};
---

<ServiceDetailLayout service={enhancedService}>
  <Fragment slot="service-content">
    <h3>Special Sets for Your Anniversary Celebration Photos</h3>

    <p>
      Anniversaries mark significant milestones in a couple's journey together,
      celebrating the years of love, growth, and memories created. These special
      occasions deserve to be commemorated with beautiful photographs that
      capture the continuing story of your relationship.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Pixxel City Studio in Nagpur, we offer premium themed sets specifically
      designed for anniversary photography. Our venue provides couples with
      beautiful, ready-made backdrops that create the perfect setting for
      romantic anniversary photos without the hassle of location scouting or
      weather concerns.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
      <img
        src="https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/Blue-Jodhpur-5.jpg?updatedAt=1737906079394"
        alt="Romantic Anniversary Set"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
      <img
        src="https://ik.imagekit.io/c54qkthzl/uploads/The_Crystal_Court_Set-1_rVfXYxGvR.JPG"
        alt="Elegant Couple Photography Set"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <h3>Why Choose Our Venue for Your Anniversary Photos?</h3>

    <h4>Romantic Themed Sets</h4>

    <p>
      We offer a diverse range of beautiful sets that can be tailored for
      anniversary celebrations. From elegant Santorini-inspired backdrops to
      intimate French cafe settings, our versatile studio spaces provide the
      perfect ambiance for capturing your continuing love story.
    </p>

    <h4>Convenient All-in-One Location</h4>

    <p>
      Instead of traveling to multiple locations, our studio provides varied
      backdrops all under one roof. This saves time and ensures you get diverse
      photos regardless of weather conditions, giving you more time to enjoy
      your anniversary celebration.
    </p>

    <h4>Complete Studio Amenities</h4>

    <p>
      Our venue offers everything needed for a comfortable photoshoot
      experience, including private changing rooms, refreshments, and
      appropriate props. You and your photographer can focus entirely on
      creating beautiful images without logistical concerns.
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg my-8 border-l-4 border-primary"
    >
      <p class="text-lg italic">
        "We celebrated our 5th anniversary with a photoshoot at Pixxel City, and
        the venue was perfect. The themed sets were beautiful and gave us such
        variety in our photos. Having access to the changing room and props made
        everything so convenient. Definitely worth booking for any special
        occasion!"
      </p>
      <cite class="block mt-4 font-medium">— Priya & Ajay, Nagpur</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <h3>Popular Anniversary Set Options</h3>

    <h4>Santorini Escape</h4>

    <p>
      Transport yourselves to the romantic Greek islands with our
      Santorini-inspired set featuring whitewashed walls, blue accents, and
      Mediterranean touches. Perfect for couples celebrating milestone
      anniversaries.
    </p>

    <h4>French Cafe</h4>

    <p>
      Create romantic Parisian memories with our charming cafe setting, complete
      with cafe tables, vintage decor, and European architectural elements that
      capture the romance of Paris.
    </p>

    <h4>Elegant Lounge</h4>

    <p>
      Our sophisticated lounge set offers a luxurious backdrop with elegant
      furniture, dramatic lighting, and upscale decor—ideal for couples wanting
      a more formal anniversary portrait setting.
    </p>

    <h3>Important Booking Information</h3>

    <p>
      Our venue provides the sets, spaces, and amenities for your anniversary
      photoshoot. You'll need to arrange for your own photographer, though we're
      happy to recommend trusted local professionals who are familiar with our
      studio spaces.
    </p>

    <p>
      We offer various time slots and package options to accommodate different
      needs and budgets. Weekend bookings fill quickly, especially during peak
      seasons, so we recommend scheduling your session at least 2-3 weeks in
      advance.
    </p>

    <p>
      A security deposit of ₹2,000 is required to confirm your booking, which is
      fully refundable after your session assuming no damage to the sets or
      props.
    </p>

    <h3>Book Your Anniversary Set Today</h3>

    <p>
      Don't let your anniversary pass without capturing beautiful memories.
      Contact Pixxel City Studio to schedule your anniversary photoshoot venue
      booking and create lasting images of this important milestone in your
      relationship.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
</ServiceDetailLayout>
